    "While ChatGPT4-RAG demonstrates significant advances over previous AI versions, medicolegal considerations dictate that a 75% full accuracy rate is insufficient for independent clinical decision-making.",
    "AI should serve to support and confirm clinician decisions rather than generate them.",
